        </item>
        <item>
            <title>半入耳式主動降噪耳機   Redmi Buds 6s 主打 14.2mm 超大動圈單元</title>
            <link>https://unwire.hk/2024/06/10/redmi-buds-6s/mobile-music/headphones/?utm_source=rss&#038;utm_medium=rss&#038;utm_campaign=redmi-buds-6s</link>
            <comments>https://unwire.hk/2024/06/10/redmi-buds-6s/mobile-music/headphones/#respond</comments>
            <dc:creator>
                <![CDATA[唐美鳳]]>
            </dc:creator>
            <pubDate>Mon, 10 Jun 2024 03:00:38 +0000</pubDate>
            <category>
                <![CDATA[音樂耳機]]>
            </category>
            <category>
                <![CDATA[Redmi Buds 6S]]>
            </category>
            <guid isPermaLink="false">https://unwire.hk/?p=1241824</guid>
            <description>
                <![CDATA[<p>小米昨日在中國發表 Redmi Buds 6S 半入耳式主動降噪耳機，它的賣點之一是配備 14.2 mm 超大動圈單元和 0.45 mm 超大振幅，小米表示耳機取得了網易的雲音超清音質認證。耳機具備半入耳主動降噪功能，提供兩種降噪模式，並支援雙咪高峯 AI 通話防風噪，最高可抵禦 9m/s 的風噪。</p><p><span id="more-1241824"></span></p><p>Redmi Buds 6S 亦配備 SoundID 訂制音效、自動調節聽感優化和空間音效，以達至平衡的音質輸出。Redmi Buds 6S 提供空間音效功能，但需要搭配 Redmi K70、Redmi K70 Pro、Xiaomi Mix Fold 3、Xiaomi 13、Xiaomi 13 Pro、Xiaomi 13 Ultra、Xiaomi 14 及 Xiaomi 14 Ultra 等手機使用。</p><p><a href="https://unwire.hk/?attachment_id=1241839" rel="attachment wp-att-1241839"><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1241839" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/06/06103b-694x463.jpg" alt="Redmi Buds 6S" width="694" height="463" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/06/06103b-694x463.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/06/06103b.jpg 1280w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></a></p><p>Redmi Buds 6S 的充電盒採用小方盒設計，提供晴雪白、子夜黑和星海藍三種機身顏色，耳機連同充電盒的總電池使用時間達 33 小時。耳機支援 Xiaomi Hyper Connect 音頻串流、智能雙裝置連接。Redmi Buds 6S 在小米官方網店的定價為 199 人民幣（約 219 港元），但上市的安排則尚未公佈。</p><p>資料及圖片來源：<a href="https://www.gizmochina.com/2024/06/09/redmi-buds-6s-semi-ear-active-noise-reduction-spatial-audio-unveiled/">gizmochina</a></p><br /><b>相關文章:</b><blockquote><li><a href="https://unwire.hk/2024/05/21/redmi-pad-pro-europe/notebook/tablet-notebook/?utm_source=inter&utm_medium=related&utm_campaign=rp" target="_blank">Redmi Pad Pro 平板，海外市場上市</a></li>&nbsp;<li><a href="https://unwire.hk/2024/04/18/redmi-pad-pro-fcc/notebook/tablet-notebook/?utm_source=inter&utm_medium=related&utm_campaign=rp" target="_blank">Redmi Pad Pro 通過 FCC 認證，有望短期內推出國際版</a></li>&nbsp;<li><a href="https://unwire.hk/2024/04/11/redmi-pro-pro-launched-in-china/notebook/tablet-notebook/?utm_source=inter&utm_medium=related&utm_campaign=rp" target="_blank">Redmi Pad Pro 平板中國上市   Snapdragon 7s Gen 2 處理器 12.1 吋屏幕</a></li>&nbsp;</blockquote><br /><p>The post <a href="https://unwire.hk/2024/06/10/redmi-buds-6s/mobile-music/headphones/">半入耳式主動降噪耳機   Redmi Buds 6s 主打 14.2mm 超大動圈單元</a> appeared first on <a href="https://unwire.hk">UNWIRE.HK</a>.</p>
]]>
            </description>
